sources.title: Diplomatic Passport (1954) MARSHA HUNT ♠ HONOR BLACKMAN
sources.description:
♠ 1st TIME on YouTUBE ♠
It's Friday@PizzaFLIX
Director: Gene Martel
Stars: Marsha Hunt, Paul Carpenter, Honor Blackman

There's more to this rarely-seen Crime Thriller than meets the eye when an American diplomat and his wife are ordered to London for a conference.

metadata.Plot: A diplomat and his wife arrive in London, and are soon involved in a series of confusing and sometimes frightening events that have no apparent explanation.
metadata.Actors: Marsha Hunt, Paul Carpenter, Henry Oscar
